	<h1><em>Full stack development</em></h1>
	<p>This blog session limits itself to the prerequisites of what not to expect if you are working in the present scenario it industry</p>
    <h3>Why is it necessary for the IT professionals to become FULL STACK</h3>
    <p>In the initial stages of <em>IT industry</em> the professionals used to thrive on the surplus</p>
    <p>demand of IT solutions going around.</p>
    <p>But now the in the 21st century the due to changes in consumer demands, there are some key changes taking place in the IT sector</p>
    <p>,now the consumers are throwing problems at us rather than demanding for specific solutions.</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Hence there is a rising demand for <strong>skilled It professionals</strong> in the industry today</p>
